340
00:23:15,769 --> 00:23:17,688
He said he'd pay you what you asked for.

341
00:23:23,735 --> 00:23:24,945
Hey.

342
00:23:27,322 --> 00:23:28,365
It's good money.

343
00:23:29,324 --> 00:23:30,325
We need it.

344
00:23:33,495 --> 00:23:36,915
