right?

428
00:29:49,621 --> 00:29:51,873
Birmingham, yes. It's a Christmas show.

429
00:29:51,957 --> 00:29:54,876
So, any way we could
maybe hit the road early next morning

430
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:56,795
