434
00:30:03,760 --> 00:30:04,636
Why?

435
00:30:05,595 --> 00:30:07,097
I can't breathe back here.

436
00:30:10,058 --> 00:30:11,017
What are you talking about?

437
00:30:11,101 --> 00:30:13,812
